{"tid":1831472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共太陽 721部隊 成立半週年","createTime":"2020-01-20T12:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T12:04:42.000Z","uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"60750fed4f6c8adc0c2b7e4e2398fbaa2568370e","tid":1831472,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T12:04:42.000Z","msg":"日本有黑太陽731部隊. 今日香港有共太陽721部隊<br />\n今日港共721 部隊 比 日本731 更殘暴.更滅絕人性<br />\n<br />\n以真面目示人的日本731部隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/odGGDgp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FodGGDgp.jpg&h=f936b7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以共太陽721部隊為耻而不敢露面的部隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pqzXV3v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpqzXV3v.png&h=60a76d79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仁愛的日本皇軍部隊 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0dZhbAT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0dZhbAT.jpg&h=c1eebb81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日殘忍暴淚的 共太陽721部隊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5iMjpV3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5iMjpV3.jpg&h=1359dfef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔該以後用 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共太陽721部隊</span></span> 正名呢班畜牲"}]}